OL,3,CThree charged with murder following
OL,4,Cdeath of man in Eston
OL,6,FThree people have been charged with
OL,7,Fmurder following the death of man in
OL,8,FMiddlesbrough.
OL,10,FPeter Phillips, 47, died in an
OL,11,Fincident at Ayton Crescent, Eston, at
OL,12,Faround 11pm on Saturday 23 May.
OL,13,FDetectives say he was found with a
OL,14,Fsingle gunshot wound.
OL,16,FHe has been described as the "heart
OL,17,Fand soul" of his family in a statement.
OL,19,FTwo 39-year-old men and a 38-year-old
OL,20,Fwoman have all been charged with
OL,21,Fmurder.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
